## To run the next check

When the review date comes up, run:

```
/ai-citation delta {{site_slug}}
```

The skill will load this baseline, run a fresh audit, compute deltas, auto-close any recommendations its detectors can verify, and produce a delta report at `{{storage_path}}/{{next_review_date}}-delta-report.html`.

