## What this reminder cannot guarantee

This file is the audit trail and a copy-paste reminder. It cannot make the review happen — that requires you (or a teammate) to run the slash command on or after **{{next_review_date}}**.

If the discipline isn't there, install the `schedule` skill and enroll this site for autonomous monthly delta runs:

```
/ai-citation delta {{site_slug}} --enroll-cron
```

That option only works if the schedule skill is installed in your environment.

